White Raven (Stance)
Level: Crusader 8, Warblade 8
Prerequisite: One White Raven maneuver
Initiation Action: 1 swift action
Range: 60 ft.
Area: 60-ft. radius emanation centered on you
Duration: Stance

While you are in this stance, you use your tactical knowledge and mastery to improve your allies' teamwork. If you are adjacent to one or more opponents, your allies gain a +5 bonus on attack rolls made against the opponent you are currently attacking.
